query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `viewerCursors` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `sessionCode` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `viewerIdentifier` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `cursorX` float NOT NULL,
  `cursorY` float NOT NULL,
  `cursorVisible` boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `viewerCursors_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `unique_viewer` (`sessionCode`, `viewerIdentifier`)
);
